title: Eps 52 - Resolution Proof
description:
Resolutions. We've all made one, and most of us have broken one. Will this be the year where you uphold your resolution? Find out how to end the broken resolution streak and become resolution proof. 
 In this podcast...
 1. Forgotten Gift
 2. How to Hack your Resolution
 3. A Solid Gold Nugget 
 4. ET's biggest Weakness
 and more...
